//[Reference] 'I must find her, no matter the cost.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10014500=彼女を見つけねばならん。費用は気にせんよ。
//[Reference] 'We came across each other but once, while I still wore my lepidopteran form.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10014600=1度、偶然彼女と出くわしたことがある。私がチョウチョの姿のときにね。
//[Reference] 'You may realise now the meaning of your previous tasks.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10014700=もう、前回の作業を依頼した意味が分かったんじゃないか。
//[Reference] 'There is but one avenue left—I must ask you to go to ^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10014800=最後に1つ手段が残ってる。^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;のところへ行ってくれないか。
//[Reference] 'As to why I will not go myself...let us leave that aside.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10014900=私自ら行かないワケだが…この件は置いておこう。
//[Reference] 'Have you spoken to my daughter yet?'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015000=もう娘に話したかね？
//[Reference] 'Many speak of your almost supernatural ability to locate the island's inhabitants!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015100=みんなが話してるよ。君は島の住民の場所が分かる、超能力みたいなものを持ってるとね！
//[Reference] 'I trust it might aid you in finding ^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015200=^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;を探すときに助けになるんじゃないか。
//[Reference] 'Ah! ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! That is the one!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015300=おぉ！^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！それだよ！
//[Reference] 'But...this is perhaps not quite how I had expected this meeting to work...'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015400=しかし…期待していたような再会とはほど遠いな…
//[Reference] 'Communication seems...rather difficult in this form.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015500=会話とは…この手のモノはいくぶん難しいようだ。
//[Reference] 'Perhaps you could discuss the problem further with ^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015600=^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;と問題を深く話してもらえないか？
//[Reference] 'Please hurry to ^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015700=頼む。急いで^c:1486b0;{0-daughter}^c:pop;のところへ行ってくれ。
//[Reference] 'She will know what needs to be done!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015800=あの子なら、やるべきことを知ってるさ。
//[Reference] 'Oh! Is that what I think it is?'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10015900=おぉ！これが私の考えていたモノかな？
//[Reference] 'Let us see how well this works!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016000=うまくいくか見てみよう！
//[Reference] 'I only hope it does not have entirely the opposite intended effect...'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016100=期待している効果と丸っきり反対のモノじゃないいといいが…
//[Reference] 'It is her! At last! In the flesh!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016200=彼女だ！やっとだよ！実物だよ！
//[Reference] 'More beauteous than I had ever imagined!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016300=想像していたよりずっと美しい！
//[Reference] 'I...I suspected this might happen.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016400=私は…実現するか疑心暗鬼だったよ。
//[Reference] 'All I truly wanted was the opportunity to speak to her.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016500=彼女と話すチャンスを心底求めていたんだ。
//[Reference] 'To give her my thanks.'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016600=お礼をしたかった。
//[Reference] 'Ah, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! I cannot thank you enough...'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016700=あぁ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！感謝してもしきれないよ…
//[Reference] 'We still have more to speak about, she and I, but you need worry yourself about it no more!'
staxel.village.dialogue.CursedCurator.line:10016800=話したいことはまだある。彼女も私も。だが、もう君は心配する必要ないよ。
